				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Owlbear cub's dialog after the goblin hunt celebration party. Occurs whether tieflings or raiders win, with a variation. He does not like the goblins - they captured him and made him play the chicken chase game.\r\n\r\nIn SwA, he speaks like 'little bites'. Short and staccato."
				}
